OPTO TECH CORP said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 27.84% to NT$500,927,000 from NT$694,230,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales            500,927          694,230    
YOY%             -27.84%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           7,062,719        7,673,653   
YOY%              -7.96% 
=================================================================
 